{"tid":1065020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殘忍虐兒】綁8歲女落浴缸浸凍水 日狠母及男友被控企圖謀殺","createTime":"2019-03-17T03:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T03:45:37.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f36ba2afe5a3f6b27710d18835c9aa42d1d6c3","tid":1065020,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/small/1552621953_1ecd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Fsmall%2F1552621953_1ecd.jpg&h=8957ca3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本福岡縣一名29歲女子與同居男友涉嫌虐待女兒於2月被捕，警方其後在他們的手機內發現新證據，顯示兩人綁住8歲女兒手腳後，再將她放入注滿冷水的浴缸中，任由女童留在浴缸內，警方以企圖謀殺罪名再次拘捕兩人。<br />\n相關新聞：【稚子何辜】疑丈夫有外遇致分手 狠母半夜浴缸淹死3歲女<br />\n<br />\n警方於2月首次拘捕兩人，並在一部手機內發現幾段兩人將女童浸入冷水的片段。該名母親與同齡的同居男友被指於去年12月29日，將就讀小二的8歲女童雙手反綁，並將她雙腳綁住浸入浴缸內，當時浴缸的水溫只得11℃，水深及至女童的口鼻之下。兩人之後任由女童留在浴缸內，直至女童變得慌張又失去意識後，才將她由水中救出。<br />\n警方認為兩人了解到事件的危險性，明知此舉有可能令女童死亡卻仍這樣做，故周四起訴他們企圖謀殺。女童母親向警方承認：「我知道如果我將她浸入冷水中，她有可能會死。」而該名同居男友則指：「我很後悔。」據悉他當時向警員表示，冷水浴是家教的一部份，因為「它不會留下瘀傷，別人因此不會發現」。<br />\n根據警方所指，兩人向女童定下10條「家規」，包括不可說謊、不可自私、要完成父母吩咐的事、要做應份的事等等，如果女童違規就要接受冷水浴懲罰，通常會被浸在水中幾小時。<br />\n女童受虐情況於本年1月25日獲揭發，當時女童學校有人發現她有受虐的迹象，於是通知兒童福利中心，再由中心報警。警方2月拘捕兩人後仍在調查案件，女童目前交由兒童福利中心照顧。<br />\n日本《每日新聞》"},{"pid":"94a633be614baca9be92f86d025940e4aecf1280","tid":1065020,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190316/59368470?fbclid=IwAR2bFIN7uxQHjZJubAuNx1dl6JWCrp4Y_s8hUAhTG9V3FySc7UMSm6h5nEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59368470%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2bFIN7uxQHjZJubAuNx1dl6JWCrp4Y_s8hUAhTG9V3FySc7UMSm6h5nEY&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=5f11130b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59368470%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2bFIN7uxQHjZJubAuNx1dl6JWCrp4Y_s8hUAhTG9V3FySc7UMSm6h5nEY&h=5bf88632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190316/59368470?fbclid=IwAR2bFIN7uxQHjZJubAuNx1dl6JWCrp4Y_s8hUAhTG9V3FySc7UMSm6h5nEY</a>"},{"pid":"24370a9f3ee3bc0c99cff1fc6f0d186414e27324","tid":1065020,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"水地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ac54ef0db33e2b1dccd0080d7fe848a335218a","tid":1065020,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24370a9f3ee3bc0c99cff1fc6f0d186414e27324","tid":1065020,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"水地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}